  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/news/\" rel=\"tag\">科技新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/15/illumina-inc-hi-seq-x-ten-dna-sequencing-for-a-thousand-dollars/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/315da98381508ce8b367d5c94248f7dd/crickandwatson.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n回首 10 年前，做一次 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2010/12/24/nanopore-dna-sequencing-technique-promises-entire-genome-in-minu/\">DNA 测序</a>的花费相当之高，总的加起来大约在 25 万美元左右。而这样的数字显然不利于其普及，所以研究者们一直在想方设法降低成本。时至今日，我们终于从 Illumina 那里听到了一个十分令人振奋的消息，他们最新推出的 HiSeq X Ten 测序仪直接把每次 DNA 测序的花费降低到了 1,000 美元（已经包括所有化学材料和硬件成本），而且这台价值 1,000 万美元的机器每年能分析成千上万的基因组。对基因研究领域来说，HiSeq X Ten 的到来可能会开启一段新的篇章。包括 Harvard-MIT Broad institute 研究所、Regeneron 制药厂等在内的多家机构已经购入了这款产品，希望能尽早看到他们的成果吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/15/illumina-inc-hi-seq-x-ten-dna-sequencing-for-a-thousand-dollars/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/matthewherper/2014/01/14/the-1000-genome-arrives-for-real-this-time/\" target=\"_blank\">Forbes</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://finance.yahoo.com/news/illumina-introduces-hiseq-x-ten-165600565.html\" target=\"_blank\">Yahoo Finance</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/15/illumina-inc-hi-seq-x-ten-dna-sequencing-for-a-thousand-dollars/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20808901/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/15/illumina-inc-hi-seq-x-ten-dna-sequencing-for-a-thousand-dollars/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
